# Nodep
---
A lightweight dependency injection framework for Node.js.

[![Travis](https://img.shields.io/travis/BrainBacon/Nodep.svg)]()

# Installation
``` bash
npm install --save nodep
```

# Usage

```js
var $p = require('nodep')();
$p.load([
    './routes'
]);
```

